  <h1>Privacy Policy for Music Market Place</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

  <p>Music Market Place ("we", "our", or "us") respects the privacy of our users ("you") and is committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and protection of your information.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not collect any personal data</strong> from users of the Music Market Place app. We only use the tools and services provided by the Pi Network SDK for authentication and payments.</p>

  <h2>2. Authentication and Payments</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> Handled entirely through the Pi Network SDK. We do not store or manage any login credentials.</li>
    <li><strong>Payments:</strong> Processed exclusively using the Pi Network SDK. We do not handle or store any financial or payment data.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Usage</h2>
  <p>Since we do not collect user data, we do not use, process, or share any personal information.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
  <p>We do not share any user data with third parties, as no data is collected.</p>

  <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Music Market Place does not target or knowingly collect personal data from children under the age of 13.</p>

  <h2>6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new effective date.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:11012brianmwaniki@gmail.com">11012brianmwaniki@gmail.com</a></p>
